snippet.title: Front Mission 5: The Power of Vyzov and State EX-AC!
snippet.description:
Apparently I got State, the best SG in the game from completing the 50th floor of Survival Simulator. I remodeled it to State EX-AC which has 3 attack sequences!

So here it is the power of State EX-AC combined with Vyzov in the Arena. I can easily beat the enemy with high odds. Nice isn't it?
